nds i need to apply so much less to achieve the color payoff i want in my makeup — purrmeow totalbeautycom member herbal essences hello hydration in moisturizing shampoo and conditioner average rating why its lifechanging this product works very well in the wintertime when your hair needs moisture but you dont have the time to shampoo then rinse then apply conditioner then rinse again also it does not make your hair look oily like some conditioners do it works well on taming frizz too — lisak totalbeautycom member aveeno daily moisturizing lotion average rating why its lifechanging i asked the pharmacist why so many lotions made me itch and she said that it probably was the parabens so i started trying products that did not have parabens ever since i check ingredients for parabens this is one of the few products that does not have parabens and since i started using aveeno i have had no problems it goes on nicely and blends in quickly so that your hands are not greasyfeeling it has been a lifesaver for me — irbecky totalbeautycom member urban decay eyeshadow primer potion tuszqcexswfqrvtaubaverage rating why its lifechanging i must have the oiliest lids on the planet nothing and i mean nothing ever stopped my eyeshadow from creasing even the creaseproof creased that is until i met urban decay eyeshadow primer potion i cant believe that i didnt invest in this before i still do have slight fading from blue eyeshadow and i do get creasing when i layer cream shadow on top of the primer but if i place powder shadow on top of the primer then layer on cream shadow i dont get any creasing my shadow looks like i just put it on for hours and hours — kissagain totalbeautycom member mark glow baby glow luxe hookup lip gloss average rating why its lifechanging this is one of those glorious rare products that is not only cheap but really works it has such great shine and isnt sticky at all also the colors layer over lipstick really well it also has just a little bit shimmer which is nice lastly gotta love the hookup option so the little tubes dont get lost in your purse — jackieznyc totalbeautycom member chi  inch ceramic flat iron average rating why its lifechanging this is an excellent flatiron it heats within  seconds and delivers smooth straight silky hair quickly and efficiently ive been straightening my long curly hair with this for over four years now and my hair is still shiny and healthy despite everyday use i recommend using this iron with bumble and bumble straight a siliconebased serum for best results — westwood totalbeautycom membersee all  lifechanging products on totalbeautycomviewers rate their favorite shampoos   published  next story more fashion  beauty the makeup product that really works for hiding scars theres finally an fdaapproved treatment for cellulite and we tried it  crisp fall fragrances that could become your signature scent do it like a pro  steps to perfect selftanner  skincare ingredients that reverse effects of aging drink it in winecolored accessories the best orless antiaging products my week of beauty mistakes how to look good on the go  surprising statistics about plastic surgery os summer beauty survival handbook junes best beauty buys  things philosophy founder cristina carlino knows for sure about aging what are your skin treatment options februarys best beauty buys  steps to conceal undereye circles the best november beauty buys summer beauty solutions  skincare habits you should break this winter  new tricks for clearer smoother skin oprahcom information view more fashion and beautyprivacy policy terms of use house rules dmca compliance cookies and tracking technology scams press room sweepstakes ad sales own careers career submission terms contact us helpfaq site map app index watch own app download the watch own app and access own anytime anywhere watch full episodes and live stream own whenever and wherever you want the watch own app is free and available to you as part of your own subscription 