tribution list of the oprah winfrey show oprahcom march   retrieved may    further readingedit illouz eva  oprah winfrey and the glamour of misery an essay on popular culture new york columbia university press isbn  retrieved may    oppenheimer mark may   the church of oprah winfrey and a theology of suffering the new york times retrieved may    external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to the oprah winfrey show official website oprahs angel network oprahs book club tv network the oprah winfrey show on imdb the oprah winfrey show at tvcom oprah winfrey at tvguidecom v t e daytime emmy award for outstanding talk show – the merv griffin show  dinah  dinah  the merv griffin show  donahue  donahue  donahue  donahue  the richard simmons show  this old house  – woman to woman  donahue  donahue  the oprah winfrey show  the oprah winfrey show  the oprah winfrey show  sally jessy raphael  the oprah winfrey show  the oprah winfrey show  good morning america  – the oprah winfrey show  the oprah winfrey show  the oprah winfrey show  the oprah winfrey show  the rosie odonnell show  the rosie odonnell show  the rosie odonnell show  the rosie odonnell show  the rosie odonnell show  the view  the wayne brady show  the ellen degeneres show  the ellen degeneres show  the ellen degeneres show  the ellen degeneres show  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitletheoprahwinfreyshowoldid categories s american television series american television series debutss american television seriess american television seriess american television series american television series endingsamerican television talk showsdaytime emmy award for outstanding talk show winnersenglishlanguage television programmingfirstrun syndicated television programs in the united statestelevision series by harpo productionsoprah winfreytelevision series by cbs television studiostelevision series by king world productionschicago television programshidden categories pages using citations with accessdate 